    <string name="text_feedback_instructions">
    <![CDATA[
        <p>Feedback is used to send a message and an attached log file to support teams.</p>
        <p>1. Add file provider with application package name in AndroidManifest.xml. See <b>android.support.v4.content.FileProvider</b></p>
        <p>2. Define log file name in <b>res/xml/filepaths.xml</b>. For example, </b>log</b> name is used as attached file when email is sent.</p>
        <p>3. Do not forget add emails in files <b>raw/feedback_copy_emails</b>, <b>raw/feedback_emails</b>.</p>
    ]]>
    </string>
